# Workflow

1. Import MusicBrainz dump into container `musicbrainz-db`.
2. Verify data presence (recording > 0).
3. Run `sql/init/00_schema.sql` to create schema `allfeat_kpi`.
4. Run `scripts/apply_views.ps1` to apply all KPI views (10+ views).
5. Run `scripts/tests.sql` for full validation (schema, views, performance).
6. Connect Excel/ODBC to `allfeat_kpi` for Power Query analysis.
7. Never modify or delete data in schema `musicbrainz`.
